reviewText: The seller was great. Pulp Fiction. Great, but Jackie Brown& reservoir dogs terrible. No fault of the seller of course, so I'm giving 4stars to be fair
Good for the money I paid. Good quality.
How can you go wrong with Tarantino's first three films?  Not a ton of special features, though.
Inner plastic holder was broken off and loose inside the case but the movies aren't scratched up too bad and it came in a timely manner.  Great movies to group together
